IMPLEMENTATION NOTES:
─────────────────────
When analyzing actual race cards:
1. Extract all relevant data from program PDF
2. Apply all adjustments systematically  
3. Build pace scenario first, then integrate figures
4. Identify value discrepancies
5. Construct logical wagering structures
6. Maintain discipline - pass races without conviction

This system prioritizes analytical rigor over speculation. When factors conflict, default to the weight of evidence rather than forcing selections.

Professional handicapping is probability assessment, not prediction. Respect uncertainty while exploiting measurable edges.
